---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Mission & Philosophy">
  <section class="py-20 bg-surface-sand">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Mission & Philosophy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-slate leading-relaxed">
        Our three-fold commitment guides everything we do: nurturing children, supporting parents, and empowering our teachers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-brand-navy max-w-none text-text-ink leading-relaxed">
        <h2>For the Children</h2>
        <p>
          We provide the highest quality care and educational opportunities in a safe, warm, and inviting environment. Children learn best through play and exploration, which is why we cultivate spaces that encourage curiosity, creativity, and social development.
        </p>

        <h2>For the Parents</h2>
        <p>
          We are committed to peace of mind. By partnering closely with families, we ensure each child's individual needs are met. We maintain open lines of communication so parents always feel connected to their child's day.
        </p>

        <h2>For our Teachers</h2>
        <p>
          Milestones respects the critical role of early childhood educators. We strive to provide a positive, collaborative workplace where teachers are valued, supported with professional development, and equipped with the resources they need to inspire young minds.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-12 border-surface-mist" />

        <div class="bg-surface-sand p-8 rounded-2xl border border-surface-mist text-center">
          <h3 class="mt-0">Join Our Team</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">We are always looking for passionate educators to join the Milestones family.</p>
          <a href="/about/careers" class="btn-primary inline-flex no-underline text-white">View Open Positions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
